{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2019-02-04/yoga-knowledge","result":{"data":{"post":{"id":"9f2d2b36-7ad9-52c2-b7f0-d69c54fe3a97","html":"<p>  呼吸，看似非常自然的一种现象，为何在瑜伽中如此重要呢？</p>\n<p>个人理解：通过呼吸，可以唤醒对内在自我的觉知。</p>\n<p>除了我们熟悉的自然呼吸，还有腹式呼吸或称隔膜呼吸、肋间呼吸或称胸式呼吸、锁骨呼吸或称肩式呼吸、完全式呼吸，见下图。</p>\n<p>  瑜伽体式配合呼吸，可参考以下原则：</p>\n<p>  起为吸，落为呼；</p>\n<p>  开为吸，合为呼；</p>\n<p>  前屈为呼，还原为吸；</p>\n<p>  后弯为呼，还原为吸；</p>\n<p>  体转为呼，还原为吸；</p>\n<p>  侧弯为呼，还原为吸；</p>\n<p>  挤压为呼，还原为吸。</p>\n<p><figure><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/01bea45cdba6648c60191ce3b16ea618/9d76a/2-%E7%91%9C%E4%BC%BD%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 33.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2         \"\n        title=\"2         \"\n        src=\"/static/01bea45cdba6648c60191ce3b16ea618/5a190/2-%E7%91%9C%E4%BC%BD%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/01bea45cdba6648c60191ce3b16ea618/772e8/2-%E7%91%9C%E4%BC%BD%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F.png 200w,\n/static/01bea45cdba6648c60191ce3b16ea618/e17e5/2-%E7%91%9C%E4%BC%BD%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F.png 400w,\n/static/01bea45cdba6648c60191ce3b16ea618/5a190/2-%E7%91%9C%E4%BC%BD%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F.png 800w,\n/static/01bea45cdba6648c60191ce3b16ea618/9d76a/2-%E7%91%9C%E4%BC%BD%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F.png 829w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-wi